						<div class="postbody">The reason to not code in asm is that the cost outweighs the benefit in most cases. You spend time doing the asm and you end up with something worse than before. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optimization_%28computer_science%29%23When_to_optimize" class="postlink">Premature optimization</a> is a root of evil.</div>

